"Tool call switched to '{0}'. You are in a specialized toolset mode. You must"
" call 'specialized_workflow_finished' when done to restore the full set of "
"APIs."
msgstr ""
"Rīka izsaukums pārslēgts uz '{0}'. Jūs atrodaties specializētā rīkkopas "
"režīmā. Jums jāizsauc 'specialized_workflow_finished', kad esat pabeidzis, "
"lai atjaunotu pilnu API kopu."

